data.description: Assumable Mortgage at 2.85%!!!   This updated pool home has a huge yard - almost half an acre with a sprinkler system to make yard maintenance easy.  The backyard is completely fenced with a double gate to park your boat, RV and all your toys.  There are also 2 storage sheds, a gazebo and the refinished pool has a handicap lift.  Inside you will find many updates including new luxury vinyl flooring, new paint, upgraded appliances and a newer AC system.  The septic system was replaced in 2022 and the roof was replaced in 2020.  There are two living areas - a front living room and dining room area and a kitchen and family room that has a vaulted ceiling and stone fireplace.  There is a huge bonus room to the rear that has floor to ceiling glass windows that look out over the backyard and pool.  The kitchen has granite counter tops and new stainless steel appliances.  This house is located in a great quiet neighborhood that is close to everything.  Bonus for the buyer - there is an assumable mortgage with just under $200,000 left on the balance at 2.85% for the remaining 27 years.
